      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dents, fading clear coat, and areas of surface rust. Mechanically, the car is currently running rough and likely needs major engine or transmission repairs in the near future. The interior has seen better days, with visible tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This is a project car or a parts vehicle for someone with the time and resources to invest in a total restoration.",
