      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it is honestly in such great shape! It runs smoothly, looks wonderful, and has been kept up with so much care over the years. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come by and take it for a test drive\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
