    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure long-term structural integrity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction and corner-exit rotation. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping characteristics, offering a communicative chassis feel and sharp turn-in. Finished in a classic colorway with minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, this vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the purist seeking a driver-centric analog experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
