    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and a well-preserved enthusiast car. The exterior finish retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye will spot a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest evidence of its time on the open road. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery remains supple and supportive, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained; it recently received a fresh set of premium all-season tires and a comprehensive fluid service. The engine pulls smoothly through the gears, the brakes are firm, and the suspension remains quiet over bumps. It includes a complete service log and two sets of keys. If you are looking for a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been cared for by a meticulous owner, this is it.",
      "price": 34500.0,
